screen_desc: The screenshot displays a mobile app interface with various account management options. At the top, there are sections for "Subscription" and "Drive with Xanh SM." Below, users can find options for "Payment," "Invoice information," and "Saved places." Further down, there are links to "Terms and Policies," "Map Contribution," "Support center," "Driver feedback," and "About us." At the bottom, there are contact options including an email and phone number, along with a "Change passcode" feature. The navigation bar at the bottom includes icons for "Home," "Activity," "Notification," and "Account."
